flowchart TD
    I[Intent\n(Human / Workflow / Agent)] --> A[Authority]
    A --> E[AEO]
    E --> V[Validator]
    V --> XB[Execution Boundary]
    XB --> P[Proof]
    P --> R[Registry]
    R --> O[Observability]

    OX[Observability Layer\n(Telemetry / Dashboards / Aggregation)] -->|may observe| O
    OX -->|may aggregate| O
    OX -->|may render| O

    OX -. may not authorize .-> A
    OX -. may not validate .-> V
    OX -. may not execute .-> XB
    OX -. may not create proof .-> P
